sub_title: 4XOlympic Athlete-My school for life: Education through sport/Startup Investor/Mentor
summary:
Reina-Flor Okori is a 4x Olympian with over 20 years on the track representing France and Equatorial Guinea. Using her sports legacy and African soul blueprint, Reina inspires and coaches international businesses, executives, and athletes to redefine the new psychology of winning and leading. 

Contact Reina today to fulfill your maximum potential with the gold medal mentality using the three pillars of performance which are Physical, Nutritional, and Mental Health.


PORTFOLIO
➣ Clients include: CEO's, Executives, MBA candidates, Global athletes
➣ Brands: Orange, PUMA, Adidas, Weleda,etc.

SERVICES
➣ Thought leadership, and soft-skills for Sports Management
➣ Communication and branding 
➣ Personal marketing strategy
➣ Career management
